### Update note by ID (happy path)
PATCH {{BASE_URL}}/notes/{{NOTE_ID}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated note title",
  "content": "Updated from api/notes/update-note.http"
}

### Update note with empty title (expected 400)
PATCH {{BASE_URL}}/notes/{{NOTE_ID}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "title": "   "
}

### Update note with invalid ID format (expected 400)
PATCH {{BASE_URL}}/notes/not-a-number
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "title": "Will not be parsed because ID is invalid"
}
